    "body": "\"We should 100% remove explicit join.  When somebody is added to an ad-hoc group chat, they should immediately be landed in the group chat. No need for the user to explicitly join, or perform any other action.  This is possible because of mutual contacts, only mutual contacts can be added to an ad-hoc group chat. If somebody is not a mutual contact, they cannot be added to an ad-hoc group chat. No exceptions\" @John-44 \r\n",
